  "format": "Sean, Amanda, and Chris report back from SXSW with verdicts on 'Us,' 'Long Shot,' 'Booksmart,' and 'The Beach Bum,' then Sean talks to Sebastián Lelio about remaking his own film for Julianne Moore.",
  "segments": [
