          "title": "Us",
          "year": 2019,
          "note": "Jordan Peele's follow-up to Get Out, with Lupita Nyong'o and Winston Duke as a family confronted by doppelgängers on a Santa Cruz beach vacation"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "discussion",
